#: ../../user/configuration.md:1
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr "設定"

#: ../../user/configuration.md:3
msgid ""
"`@nagatatz/rescript-vitest` is a thin binding layer with no settings of "
"its own. Configuration happens in two places: the ReScript compiler and "
"Vitest."
msgstr ""
"`@nagatatz/rescript-vitest` は薄いバインディング層で、独自の設定はありません。"
"設定は ReScript コンパイラと Vitest の 2 か所で行います。"

#: ../../user/configuration.md:6
msgid "ReScript (`rescript.json`)"
msgstr "ReScript（`rescript.json`）"

#: ../../user/configuration.md:8
msgid ""
"Compile in source to ESM so Vitest can run the output directly, and list "
"the package as a dependency so the bindings are compiled:"
msgstr ""
"Vitest が出力を直接実行できるよう in-source で ESM にコンパイルし、"
"バインディングがコンパイルされるようパッケージを依存に追加します:"

