msgstr "フェイクタイマー"

#: ../../user/configuration.md:57
msgid ""
"Fake-timer behaviour (used by `Vi.useFakeTimers`) is Vitest's own "
"configuration; see the [Vitest fake timers "
"guide](https://vitest.dev/guide/mocking.html#timers)."
msgstr ""
"フェイクタイマーの挙動（`Vi.useFakeTimers` が利用）は Vitest 自体の設定です。"
"[Vitest フェイクタイマーガイド](https://vitest.dev/guide/mocking.html#timers) を参照してください。"

